item.title: Faith before basketball for Yeshiva University champions
item.description: NEW YORK (AP) — Every of the mighty Maccabees has his role on the men’s basketball personnel. Gabriel Leifer sinks three-pointers; Daniel Katz is the protection wizard; Simcha Halpert makes the correct alley-oop passes to Ryan Turell who soars for dunks.
